-- England Names Bowler Chris Tremlett in Cricket Performance Squad
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2013-04-02T14:33:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-02/england-names-bowler-chris-tremlett-in-cricket-performance-squad.html
Fast-bowler Chris Tremlett was named
in  England ’s 30-man performance squad for the 2013 summer
season.  The injury-hit Surrey player hasn’t appeared in a Test
since January last year. England’s schedule includes two Tests
against New Zealand and an Ashes series against  Australia .  England performance squad: A. Cook (Test and one-day 
captain), Stuart Broad (Twenty20 captain), J. Anderson, J. 
Bairstow, I. Bell, R. Bopara, T. Bresnan, D. Briggs, J. Buttler,
N. Compton, J. Dernbach, S. Finn, A. Hales, J. Harris, C.
Kieswetter, M. Lumb, S. Meaker, E. Morgan, G. Onions, M.
Panesar, S. Patel, K. Pietersen, M. Prior, J. Root, G. Swann, J.
Tredwell, C. Tremlett, J. Trott, C. Woakes, L. Wright.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  